    "The term \"medical and psychological rehabilitation\" has recently gained popularity and spread.",
    "The concept of \"rehabilitation\" appeared in 1844 in the international practice.",
    "It was used to denote measures aimed not only at treatment but also at restoring body functions in order to improve the quality of life.",
    "After the First World War, medical, recreational and social rehabilitation services became available to military veterans due to the efforts of the Red Cross charity.",
    "In the modern world, the issues of rehabilitation of this category of people have become an important aspect of social policy."
